{"tid":646616,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滬百億建硬X射線激光裝置","createTime":"2018-04-29T08:14:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T09:28:42.000Z","uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce1c68a117cb550503fd90df2bb3bf88881c269f","tid":646616,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:14:07.000Z","msg":"滬百億建硬X射線激光裝置<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20180429/s00055/86327c4fceee9bc8a84e60b7cb6677cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20180429%2Fs00055%2F86327c4fceee9bc8a84e60b7cb6677cb.jpg&h=ff5c36e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「硬X射線自由電子激光裝置」上周五在張江科學城內開始動工。（網上圖片）<br />\n圖1之1 - 「硬X射線自由電子激光裝置」上周五在張江科學城內開始動工。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】投資近百億元人民幣的科學基建「硬X射線自由電子激光裝置」啟動儀式前日在上海科技大學舉行，估計7年後落成。該激光裝置由上海市政府及中國科學院合作建成，選址於張江科學城內，全個裝置總長約3.1公里。<br />\n<br />\n工程建設一台能量8Ge V超導直線加速器、3條波蕩器線、3條光速線及10個實驗室。項目包括束流診斷、控制、激光、同步、數據收集以及公共設施等配套，有望成為全球最高效及最先進的自由電子激光裝置之一，成為物理、化學、能源科學等多個學科的研究平台。<br />\n<br />\n（中新社）"},{"pid":"45487dda37d91469ab1ff011a214c770cc4883b3","tid":646616,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"use which country chipset?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7deb4e27cb82a34f584b10476a1ac5da929a7fd0","tid":646616,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:47:18.000Z","msg":"唔係好明咩波蕩器、硬X射"},{"pid":"c3ce7ee35c2e26a7715af1c765ed71913e5fb026","tid":646616,"uid":68,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:51:07.000Z","msg":"硬膠射線"},{"pid":"d1aa2cd8a82e42f4f8df110abac205e832cbe860","tid":646616,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T08:59:53.000Z","msg":"X=9 ?"},{"pid":"9adf2c06a0c68de1ddf3edea7ca55da8762fef41","tid":646616,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T09:03:17.000Z","msg":"硬膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi